# 🔹 Common GATE Traps

### Trap 1

[
a^*
]

contains ε.

---

### Trap 2

[
a^+
]

does **not** contain ε.

---

### Trap 3

Regular Expressions cannot recognize **Context-Free Languages**.

---

### Trap 4

Every DFA has an equivalent Regular Expression.

---

### Trap 5

Arden's Theorem applies only when **ε is not part of P**.

---

# 📝 Formula Sheet

| Concept          | Formula                           |
| ---------------- | --------------------------------- |
| Kleene Star      | (R^*) = Zero or more repetitions  |
| Positive Closure | (R^+ = RR^*)                      |
| Arden's Theorem  | (R = Q + RP \Rightarrow R = QP^*) |
| Regular Language | Accepted by DFA/NFA/RE            |

